title: Live at the Bell House, The Astronaut Session (Part 1)
description: At the Bell House in Brooklyn, NY on 12/18/2011 for our second show in front of a live audience. Co-host Eugene Mirman was joined by fellow comedians Kristen Schaal and John Hodgman, while Neil brought along his NASA astronaut buddy, Mike Massimino.
author: feed@startalkradio.net (Neil deGrasse Tyson)
